# FOSS & Privacy Compliance

## License

- **Apache-2.0** — see root `LICENSE`
- Adobe Lightroom Classic SDK is **not** in this repo; download separately for local dev
- No proprietary closed-source SDKs committed to the repository

## Distribution

- GitHub Releases: `NoClipAuto-v*-win64.lrdevplugin.zip` (+ macOS UNVALIDATED)
- Install path: `%APPDATA%\Adobe\Lightroom\Modules\` (Windows)

## Privacy & network

- **No network calls** in plugin or analyzer v1
- All processing is local (preview JPEG → analyzer → catalog develop settings)
- Temp preview files deleted after analysis

## Security

- Secrets never committed; run `scripts/foss-audit.ps1` before release
- Analyzer accepts file paths from plugin only — no arbitrary URL fetch
- Report vulnerabilities via `SECURITY.md`

## Lightroom SDK (Module D)

- Lua production code uses `Lr*` namespaces only
- No generic Lua `require` of non-SDK modules in shipped plugin code
- See `modules/lightroom/MODULE.md`
